de: Annex to the Financial Management Agreement between contributing Nations and the Nato-IS Office of Financial Control for the Support of the Building Integrity and reducing corruption risk in defence establishments Trust Fund  - 10-12-2013 - Ausführungs- und Finanzverwaltungsabkommen zwischen der Schweizerischen Eidgenossenschaft, Polen, dem Vereinigten Königreich und dem Internationalen Sekretariat der NATO betreffend des Fonds für spezielle Verwendungszwecke im Bereich der Verstärkung der Integrität und der Reduktion von Korruptionsrisiken in den Verteidigungsinstitutionen
en: Annex to the Financial Management Agreement between contributing Nations and the Nato-IS Office of Financial Control for the Support of the Building Integrity and reducing corruption risk in defence establishments Trust Fund  - 10-12-2013 - Executing Agent Agreement and Financial Management Agreement between Switzerland, Poland and the United Kingdom and the NATO office of financial control for the support of the building integrity and reducing corruption risk in defence establishments trust fund (PfP Trust Fund Building Integrity)
fr: Annex to the Financial Management Agreement between contributing Nations and the Nato-IS Office of Financial Control for the Support of the Building Integrity and reducing corruption risk in defence establishments Trust Fund  - 10-12-2013 - Accord d'exécution et accord de gestion des finances entre la Confédération suisse, la Pologne, le Royaume-Uni et le Secrétariat international de l'OTAN concernant le fonds d'affectation spéciale en matière de renforcement de l'intégrité et de réduction du risque de corruption dans les institutions de défense
